| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6740 — Recovery Inhibition (medusalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d8cccb3b-a873-56c4-918f-3ed1a06d426f"
